Kernel Modules
	$ kldstat --> show loaded modules
	$ kldload <module> --> load kernel modules

Kernel Settings

	$ sysctl
		--> get, set or tune values from kernel (similar to proc in linux)
	$ sysctl parameter=value
		--> set value for running kernel (e.g. max open files...)
	Make permanent changes in th /etc/sysctl.conf file